<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١١٦]</span> فى النحل: <span style="color:#947721">{وَبِنِعْمَتِ اللهِ هُمْ يَكْفُرُونَ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[النحل:٧٢]</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وفى العنكبوت:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{وَبِنِعْمَةِ اللهِ يَكْفُرُونَ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[العنكبوت:٦٧]</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١١٧]</span> فى النحل: <span style="color:#947721">{وَلا تَكُ فِي ضَيْقٍ مِمّا يَمْكُرُونَ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[النحل:١٢٧]</span> وفى النمل: <span style="color:#947721">{وَلا تَكُنْ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[النمل:٧٠]</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١١٨]</span> فى الحج: <span style="color:#947721">{كُلَّما أَرادُوا أَنْ يَخْرُجُوا مِنْها مِنْ غَمٍّ أُعِيدُوا فِيها}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[الحج:٢٢]</span>.<span style="color:#006d98"> وليس فى سجدة لقمان:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{مِنْ غَمٍّ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[السجدة:٢٠]</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١١٩]</span> فى الحج: <span style="color:#947721">{وَأَنَّ ما يَدْعُونَ مِنْ دُونِهِ هُوَ الْباطِلُ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[الحج:٦٢]</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وفى لقمان:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{وَأَنَّ ما يَدْعُونَ مِنْ دُونِهِ الْباطِلُ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[لقمان:٣٠]</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١٢٠]</span> فى الشعراء: <span style="color:#947721">{ما تَعْبُدُونَ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[الشعراء:٧٠]</span>.<span style="color:#006d98"> وفى الصافات:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{ماذا تَعْبُدُونَ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[الصافات:٨٥]</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١٢١]</span> فى النمل: <span style="color:#947721">{وَمَنْ شَكَرَ فَإِنَّما يَشْكُرُ لِنَفْسِهِ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[النحل:٤٠]</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وفى لقمان:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{وَمَنْ يَشْكُرْ فَإِنَّما يَشْكُرُ لِنَفْسِهِ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[لقمان:١٢]</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١٢٢]</span> فى القصص: <span style="color:#947721">{يَبْسُطُ الرِّزْقَ لِمَنْ يَشاءُ مِنْ عِبادِهِ وَيَقْدِرُ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[القصص:٨٢]</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وفى العنكبوت وسبأ:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{وَيَقْدِرُ لَهُ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[سبأ:٣٩]</span> <span style="color:#947721">{وَيَقْدِرُ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[العنكبوت:٦٢]</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١٢٣]</span> فى سأل سائل: <span style="color:#947721">{وَالَّذِينَ فِي أَمْوالِهِمْ حَقٌّ مَعْلُومٌ لِلسّائِلِ وَالْمَحْرُومِ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[المعارج ٢٤،٢٥]</span>.<span style="color:#006d98"> وليس فى الذاريات:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«معلوم»</span> <span style="color:#707070">[الذاريات:١٩]</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١٢٤]</span> فى النازعات: <span style="color:#947721">{يَوْمَ يَتَذَكَّرُ الْإِنْسانُ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[النازعات:٣٥]</span>.<span style="color:#006d98"> وفى الفجر:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span style="color:#947721">{يَوْمَئِذٍ يَتَذَكَّرُ الْإِنْسانُ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[الفجر:٢٣]</span>.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
