<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span style="color:#947721">{وَالصّابِئِينَ وَالنَّصارى}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[الحج:١٧]</span>.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
